:0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T15:25:36.000Z","msg":"睇下同邊個<br />\n<br />\n同d西女人坐得差小小都西成程飯 <br />\n<br />\n同兄弟就是撚但 最緊要食得開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"537ff110160c73ecb6b2e63f15b80aede82961df","tid":668673,"uid":153400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T15:33:37.000Z","msg":"同埋依家人大咗,只會去返食開個幾間,習慣咗個環境,伙計都認得,沒興趣揾新野"},{"pid":"f4c236c0fe59fdd269775f0f42a8ffcfcc2d6ef0","tid":668673,"uid":51932,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T15:38:40.000Z","msg":"廁所都好緊要，香港好撚多門面唔錯，廁所就爛到呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"573c963037002283bf8e1d49ba0315aba61c25ff","tid":668673,"uid":24998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T15:43:33.000Z","msg":"雖然認同坐射舒服好重要<br />\n但對茶木呢間野都係好撚抗拒<br />\n係就係任你坐<br />\n但真係食都食唔飽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c027e628b0562fecfaebdbb02f8989d2002c32f","tid":668673,"uid":24998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"573c963037002283bf8e1d49ba0315aba61c25ff","tid":668673,"uid":24998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T15:43:33.000Z","msg":"雖然認同坐射舒服好重要<br />\n但對茶木呢間野都係好撚抗拒<br />\n係就係任你坐<br />\n但真係食都食唔飽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T15:43:45.000Z","msg":"*坐得"},{"pid":"3fca99e8c1676a87722e1465c3c61bd421f949f9","tid":668673,"uid":74302,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"aadd76dafdb4cd2f4c1af5119bcd81f957238776","tid":668673,"uid":176318,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T01:25:34.000Z","msg":"我仲有心大力<br />\n<br />\n樓主,講下邊D餐廳坐得辛苦,冷氣又唔夠 又偏僻,但又好食既餐廳?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T15:57:03.000Z","msg":"澳牛算唔算係呢類？"},{"pid":"13ac806fcf5e92d655449004306bada9d2a39df4","tid":668673,"uid":55093,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T15:59:08.000Z","msg":"硬係有D朋友覺得環境越差越有風味<br />\n